50
00:10:15,658 --> 00:10:17,243
<i>since the Dow Jones opened
this morning.</i>

51
00:10:17,535 --> 00:10:19,203
<i>Tina Lamberg reports.</i>

52
00:10:19,495 --> 00:10:21,455
<i>Gas prices are up 16¢.</i>

53
00:10:21,747 --> 00:10:25,000
<i>Regular grade is averaging 2.68
per gallon across the country,</i>

54
00:10:25,292 --> 00:10:27,711
<i>with expected gains even higher
through the long weekend.</i>

55
00:10:28,003 --> 00:10:29,672
<i>Now traffic and transit
on the threes.</i>

56
00:10:29,964 --> 00:10:32,424
<i>We have delays
up to one half hour,</i>

57
00:10:32,716 --> 00:10:34,051
<i>and an accident
early this morning</i>

58
00:10:34,343 --> 00:10:35,928
<i>leaves Jericho Turnpike
