282
00:24:09,199 --> 00:24:10,200
<i>Mom!</i>

283
00:24:10,492 --> 00:24:12,285
<i>I'm downstairs.</i>

284
00:24:12,577 --> 00:24:13,828
<i>She says she's downstairs.</i>

285
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:15,413
<i>Where are you, daddy?</i>

286
00:24:15,705 --> 00:24:17,248
