where I am, kiddo.

287
00:24:17,540 --> 00:24:18,540
<i>No, I don't.</i>

288
00:24:18,708 --> 00:24:19,876
Sure, you do.

289
00:24:20,168 --> 00:24:21,670
<i>You're calling from the plane?</i>

290
00:24:21,962 --> 00:24:23,088
You've got it.

291
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,423
<i>Mom!
Dad's calling from the plane!</i>

292
00:24:25,715 --> 00:24:26,841
<i>Sweetie, I can't hear you.</i>

293
00:24:27,133 --> 00:24:28,635
<i>He's on the plane right now.</i>

294
00:24:28,927 --> 00:24:30,136
