411
00:29:12,961 --> 00:29:20,468
♪♪

412
00:30:16,733 --> 00:30:19,193
[CLOCK TICKING]

413
00:32:04,215 --> 00:32:06,592
[DOOR OPENS]

414
00:32:06,884 --> 00:32:09,011
[DOOR SHUTS]

415
00:32:09,303 --> 00:32:12,557
[SEAGULLS SHRIEKING]

416
00:32:25,278 --> 00:32:27,071
[SQUEALS]

417
00:32:27,363 --> 00:32:29,866
[ENGINE TURNS OVER]

418
00:32:55,308 --> 00:32:56,851
[HORN HONKS LOUDLY]

419
00:33:09,197 --> 00:33:11,616
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

420
00:33:19,832 --> 00:33:21,334
[KNOCKING]

421
00:33:29,258 --> 00:33:31,219
Hello?

422
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:03,500
Hey.

423
00:34:03,626 --> 00:34:04,335
Oh!

424
00:34:04,627 --> 00:34:06,337
I'm so sorry.

425
00:34:06,629 --> 00:34:08,089
Hi.
I'll just be a sec.

426
00:34:08,381 --> 00:34:09,715
Okay.

427
00:34:10,007 --> 00:34:11,842
Whoo!
Sorry, I didn't see you there.

428
00:34:12,134 --> 00:34:15,179
Guess I had too much coffee.

429
00:34:15,471 --> 00:34:17,974
Boy, this place
is just looking beautiful.

430
00:34:18,266 --> 00:34:20,643
She always finds
the most interesting things.

431
00:34:20,935 --> 00:34:23,563
I'm such a dodo
when it comes to plants.

432
00:34:23,854 --> 00:34:25,439
I'm always so jealous of people

433
00:34:25,731 --> 00:34:27,733
