I'll talk to you later.

813
01:06:55,763 --> 01:06:57,264
- Bye-bye.
- <i>Don't you dare-</i>

814
01:06:57,556 --> 01:06:59,225
[BEEP]

815
01:07:02,019 --> 01:07:03,562
