907
01:19:41,361 --> 01:19:42,361
<i>It's me.</i>

908
01:19:42,404 --> 01:19:43,113
<i>I can't hear you.</i>

909
01:19:43,405 --> 01:19:44,447
<i>Don't hang up.</i>

910
01:19:44,739 --> 01:19:45,448
<i>Can you hear me?
