911
01:19:45,740 --> 01:19:46,992
<i>Where are you?</i>

912
01:19:47,284 --> 01:19:49,303
<i>Hold on; I'm going to try
to move a different place.</i>

913
01:19:49,327 --> 01:19:50,495
<i>John.
John, where are you?</i>

914
01:19:50,787 --> 01:19:52,622
<i>I'm still at the airport.
I'm still here.</i>

915
01:19:52,914 --> 01:19:54,434
<i>But I'm leaving.
