916
01:19:54,666 --> 01:19:55,666
<i>Can you hear me?</i>

917
01:19:55,875 --> 01:19:57,235
<i>I'm calling to tell you
that I'm...</i>

918
01:19:57,377 --> 01:19:59,462
<i>I can't hear you.
I can't.</i>

919
01:19:59,754 --> 01:20:00,922
<i>I'm going to hang up.</i>

920
01:20:01,214 --> 01:20:03,800
[BROKEN] <i>Sweetheart.
Sweetheart.</i>

921
01:20:04,092 --> 01:20:06,636
<i>If you can hear me, John...</i>

922
01:20:06,928 --> 01:20:09,889
<i>Call back.</i>

923
01:20:10,181 --> 01:20:12,392
<i>I'm going to hang up.
Bye.</i>

924
01:20:12,684 --> 01:20:13,684
[JET ENGINE ROARING]

925
01:20:13,727 --> 01:20:15,854
<i>Bye-bye.</i>

926
01:20:31,536 --> 01:20:34,331
