Oh, my God.
Oh, my God!

929
01:20:58,063 --> 01:20:59,103
Oh, my God, it's gorgeous.

930
01:20:59,314 --> 01:21:00,357
It's gorgeous.

931
01:21:00,648 --> 01:21:02,108
